item.title: WordCamp Sydney 2024
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
sydney.wordcamp.org/2024

What is WordCamp Sydney?

WordCamp Sydney is a volunteer-run and not-for-profit two-day conference for designers, developers, marketers, business owners, and anyone using WordPress or any website.

What can I do at WordCamp Sydney?

WordCamp Sydney features two action-packed days of talks from industry experts and community members sharing their knowledge. There are no sales pitches, just educational content.

There will be content for everyone regardless of your WordPress knowledge or skill level.

You can also network with hundreds of other WordPress enthusiasts and visit our sponsors to learn about their products and services.

What if I have been to a WordCamp before?

No two WordCamp experiences are the same. WordCamp Sydney offers a unique experience. Whether attending your first or 100th WordCamp, you will have fun, learn a lot, and widen your circle of WordPress friends and colleagues.
